{"tid":1855114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留喺屋企，最適合就係寫維基百科","createTime":"2020-02-01T02:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T10:30:30.000Z","uid":71237,"like":101,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9e84a31f277aac8c80bca6e38fa612d54cf44e2d","tid":1855114,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"維基百科適合使用屋企電腦寫，唔適合用手機寫。<br />\n大家可以趁住近排多咗時間留喺屋企，多啲寫維基百科。<br />\n<br />\n首先依一刻大家最想寫嘅一定係香港的疫情。大家可以紀錄低政府嘅應對到底有幾差。<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎事件香港情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/GTo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2FGTo&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=400a7cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/GTo</a><br />\n<br />\n不如留意返維基百科入面<span style=\"color: red;\">每一句</span>都必須要有「第三方可靠來源」做reference。親身經歷係唔可以寫落去。最好用新聞報導/書籍/學術論文做reference，唔好用連登、FB、專欄、YouTube。詳情可以睇下我寫嘅新手教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e41d791a960cfa30630b404a24b181a30c1dc8b","tid":1855114,"uid":71237,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"引用資料來源有兩個方法。<br />\n1. 你登記咗account嘅話，可以去去setting開啟「視覺化編輯」，跟住就可以用自動工具可以幫你引用來源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGkGH5P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGkGH5P.gif&h=23d6ce9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過依個方法唔係完美，有啲參數可能會亂咗，可能需要人手執下。<br />\n<br />\n2. 編輯原始碼，你跟依張gif圖直接輸入標題、URL、日期、報章的名稱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6L0d93.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6L0d93.gif&h=ba9c7b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始唔熟手唔緊要，總之勇敢試下先。慢慢用熟咗就會進步。"},{"pid":"11b0570ed84f460bcdfdd1679d4382e34693e9ac","tid":1855114,"uid":344033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:07:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=fff578dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=c56dd26e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=3d8a63d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手正評，避免沉底"},{"pid":"969e6e9ea520b7acbb2964658d91c01bce3262bc","tid":1855114,"uid":165699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"有用 會做"},{"pid":"5ac030c42315cd31c13ecd6635a102a44029384e","tid":1855114,"uid":13352